{"tid":1740921,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"進擊的巨人金句 教識我地如何抗爭","createTime":"2019-11-20T06:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T06:41:59.000Z","uid":5737,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"496b5dc4059537e238153d2b5dec18232c2565c5","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/i2.kknews.cc/SIG=372gj61/ctp-vzntr/3q73145r517n4qqn9so2r7s390368q7p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D372gj61%2Fctp-vzntr%2F3q73145r517n4qqn9so2r7s390368q7p.jpg&h=abdf3c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n人，只有在放棄戰鬥的時候才算輸，只要堅持戰鬥，<br />\n就還沒輸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-www.bluestacks.com/bs-images/Banner_com.gamedreamer.aotpgtw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-www.bluestacks.com%2Fbs-images%2FBanner_com.gamedreamer.aotpgtw.jpg&h=76289dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.活着就要有尊嚴的活下去，像這樣像禽獸一樣永遠被關在籠子裏苟延殘喘的活着，我寧可選擇自由的死去<br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/9547915840/1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F9547915840%2F1000&h=34187658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.<br />\n什麼都不能放棄，就什麼都改變不了。<br />\n如果想要凌駕在怪物之上，或許連人性都要放棄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-6637312847b3570b174c6559a45387a5_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic3.zhimg.com%2F50%2Fv2-6637312847b3570b174c6559a45387a5_hd.jpg&h=0e7d1619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4.<br />\n不戰鬥就會輸，戰鬥瞭可能也會死但也有可能活下來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/9230724822/641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F9230724822%2F641&h=0d65f94a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54d470b025ab9678a6c3ece48de2fddcd5526dc6","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:17:41.000Z","msg":"香港人 幾時先會明<br />\n無法舍棄任何東西的人，就無法改變任何事實！<br />\n就算有幾多個勇武都係咁"},{"pid":"ee999b5bd90b50eebbd3084948759c37fdf84709","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:18:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be6c526e77ad1e554b3e5ca29a6c4f2508977f07","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:19:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1069b231d64f3f54389e3a15489f4012fe3b8f9","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e757277f2e03f03e5c9b3a250ba0665f464d925","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:21:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8a0c92d3bc0ef0fffca15dd7cada5e5e9cffd77","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:21:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b8fc4b2a42a4c094b2789664c80ae5a84e427b4","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"725ebc601f60dd6ad831a6680135e0ddb1f37a52","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:22:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3b2cfe4006fa4d1a9a2dbbfd79d1fdf90dab9f2","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:23:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62ad933a1a8a575e02f968ed4f99fb1ca688b1c4","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:24:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b34b3ebbdb345b795e308f82a75dd6827b58e3a","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:26:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"51d75a8f4addc921202a210c5a76ffcc40cd9e7b","tid":1740921,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c74488967e4b0e8131bd06d8df4ce59f2e43a2a"